{"version":"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1","authors":[{"avatar":"https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=John+Doe","name":"John Doe","url":"https://example.com"}],"description":"Material 3-inspired Lume Blog Theme.","feed_url":"https://lume.shiraha.js.org/p/2/feed.json","home_page_url":"https://lume.shiraha.js.org/","title":"Lume Theme Shiraha","items":[{"_indieweb":{"type":"article"},"content_html":"<h2 id=\"setup-deno--lume\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#setup-deno--lume\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Setup Deno &#x26; Lume</h2>\n<p>As this is a Lume theme, please follow the <a href=\"https://deno.com/manual@v1.34.2/getting_started/installation\">Deno installation instructions</a> and <a href=\"https://lume.land/docs/overview/installation/\">Lume documentation</a> to install them first.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install-lume-theme-shiraha\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#install-lume-theme-shiraha\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Install Lume Theme Shiraha</h2>\n<p>Now that you should have a basic Lume blog, modify <span data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><code data-language=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"github-light github-dark\"><span data-line=\"\"><span>_config.ts</span></span></code></span> to use the Shiraha theme:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"diff\" data-theme=\"github-light github-dark\"><code data-language=\"diff\" data-theme=\"github-light github-dark\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">import lume from 'lume/mod.ts'</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D\">+ import lts from 'https://deno.land/x/lume_theme_shiraha/mod.ts'</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B31D28;--shiki-dark:#FDAEB7\">- const site = lume()</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D\">+ const site = lume().use(lts())</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">export default site</span></span></code></pre></figure>","date_published":"2024-01-26T13:41:03.527Z","id":"https://lume.shiraha.js.org/articles/part-1-installation/","tags":["Lume_Theme_Shiraha"],"title":"Part 1: Installation","url":"https://lume.shiraha.js.org/articles/part-1-installation/"}]}